  "ciliary_role": "Central linker subunit that helps connect the N-DRC to the outer dynein arms. Loss of DRC7 causes defects in sperm storage and fertility (31659045). Essential for the correct assembly of the N-DRC and flagella, stability of the N-DRC is essential for proper axoneme elongation. DRC7 is essential to localize DRC5 in the correct place, and that DRC5 regulates flagellar motility (31961863)",
